      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LINDENOW BUSTER (2) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from six starts. Was out of the placings last time (30.06) at Sandown in a Special conditions H, finishing sixth and beaten 6 lengths. With a clean break looks hard to beat. MATILDA ROSE (1) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 5 length third over 400m at Warragul, clocking 22.88. The form out of her last race has been franked. Well-placed to take this out. PAW REVY (5) quickly away to win over the 450m at Warrnambool two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing second at this track last start. Expected to be in the finish again. AKINA JOHNNY (8) was in the money last time at Warragul (22.95) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 1.75 lengths second. Has two wins already from this draw.",
